vim wrangler.toml

# Redeploy
npm run deploy

# Re-run analysis to validate
npm run analyze-baseline -- --endpoint https://runics.YOUR_SUBDOMAIN.workers.dev
```

### 4. Move to Phase 2

Once baseline is acceptable, begin implementing:
- Confidence gating (3-tier routing)
- LLM deep search (Tier 3)
- Async enrichment (Tier 2)
- Composition detection
